1. Close your wallet
2. Go to your PRCYcoin directory located at %appdata%/PRCYcoin
3. *VERY IMPORTANT STEP IF YOU HAVE COINS IN YOUR WALLET Backup your wallet by right clicking on wallet.dat copying it and pasting it in a different location other than your PRCYcoin directory.
4. Download the recent Bootstrap from https://mega.nz/#F!2RsDmJxT!vs5ute2JyRDCRNsb7nEcMw
5. Copy the Bootstrap file you just downloaded to the PRCYcoin directory %appdata%/PRCYcoin
6. Unzip the Bootstrap file and extract there.
7. Double click on Install-Windows.bat.  Once it finishes installing hit Enter when prompted.
8. Open your wallet
9. Done
